Barbara Marsh

F, #701524, d. 18 September 2002

Last Edited=11 Sep 2017

Barbara Marsh was the daughter of Colonel C. H. Marsh. She married Maj.-Gen. John Malcolm McNeill, son of Brig.-Gen. Angus John McNeill and Lilian Vaughan Barron, in 1939. She died on 18 September 2002.

From 1939, her married name became McNeill.

Jean Philippa Hiley1

F, #701525, d. 30 September 2002

Last Edited=11 Sep 2017

Jean Philippa Hiley was the daughter of Colonel Sir Ernest Haviland Hiley and Brenda Lee Lord.1 She married Philip Adlington Broke on 1 December 1934.1 She died on 30 September 2002 at Winchester, Hampshire, England.1

From 1 December 1934, her married name became Broke.1

Princess Faiza of Egypt1

F, #701526, b. 8 November 1923, d. 6 June 1994

Last Edited=11 Sep 2017

Princess Faiza of Egypt was born on 8 November 1923 at Cairo, Egypt.1 She was the daughter of King Fuad I of Egypt and Nazli Sabri.1,2 She married Mehmet Ali Bulent Rauf in 1945.1 She and Mehmet Ali Bulent Rauf were divorced.1 She died on 6 June 1994 at age 70 at Los Angeles, CAlifornia, U.S.A.1

From 1945, her married name became Rauf.1
